Author: finer_feelings
Text: My intake is anywhere from 600-800, which I know is impossible to gain weight off of but I’m just being paranoid. I’ve been doing some running too, on top of an active job. It must just be dysmorphia. :/ I’m sorry to hear you feel the same and thanks for the tip <3

Author: Syd_Squid24
Text: I have the same issue :( But what is your current intake? Are you exercising? Lifting moderate weights and a little cardio can help tone and possibly help you lose the last bit of fat
